About Optimum Infosystem:

Optimum Infosystem is the Indian subsidiary of global IT service company Optimum Solutions Singapore. We deliver digital services on a variety of technology platforms to enable large-scale business programmer for clients ranging from Fortune 500 companies to vibrant start-ups.
Optimum has in-house technology focused CoEs like Data Analytics, Platform and Product Engineering, Digital Infrastructure and Enterprise Solutions. We are solving high priority and niche domain problems with our digital offerings.
Founded in 1997, we currently have an employee strength of over 4000+ employees in 9 geographies (Singapore, Malaysia, Hongkong, China, USA, and UAE).  In India, we have offices in Bangalore, Chennai, Hyderabad, and Pune. We are a strategic partner for several Banks and Technology companies like Morgan Stanley, Standard Chartered Google, Credit Suisse, Citi Bank, BNPP, DELL, Walmart, Shell, Meta, Grab, PayPal, Amazon etc.
 
